Bukaannada qaba calaamadaha cudurka neefsashada ee daran waa in lagu taageeraa kor u qaadista neefsashada (ECMO), oo ah habka wadnaha oo la hagaajiyay oo loo isticmaalo daaweynta wadnaha oo halis ah ama neefsashada oo aan ku filnayn.
Intaa waxaa dheer, hagaajinta dheelitirka elektaroolka, ka hortagga iyo xakamaynta caabuqa iyo sii deynta jirka, iyo ka hortagga howlaha xubnaha jirka ayaa sidoo kale aad muhiim ugu ah bukaannada SARS-CoV-2.
Waxaa la ogyahay in duufaanta cytokine ay sabab u tahay ka-hortagga nidaamka difaaca jirka ee bukaannada SARS iyo MERS.
Duufaanta Cytokine waa nooc ka mid ah jawaabta dabiiciga ah ee nidaamka caabuqa oo ay soo bandhigtay taxane ah cytokines oo ay ka mid yihiin TNFα, IL-1β, IL-2, IL-6, IFNα, IFNβ, IFNγ, iyo MCP-1.
Cytokines-kaani waxay la socdaan unugyada difaaca inay sii daayaan tiro badan oo ah daroogooyinka aan isbedelka lahayn ee keena ARDS iyo sidoo kale burburka xubnaha badan.
Xakamaynta immunotherapy waxay muhiim u tahay in la ogaado duufaanta cytokine, gaar ahaan bukaannada aadka u daran.
Corticosteroids iyo tocilizumab, oo ah anti-IL6 monoclonal antibody, ayaa loo isticmaalay in lagu daaweeyo cytokine storm.
Daaweynta kale ee antibody-ka ee cytokine-ka waxaa ka mid ah isbeddelka iyo jawaabta tooska ah ee T-sel antibody; IFN-γ, IL-1, iyo TNF inhibition; JAK inhibitor; blinatumomab; cytokine-ka calaamadeynta 4-ka; iyo HDAC inhibitors.
Steroids, sida immunosuppressants, ayaa si weyn loogu isticmaalay daaweynta SARS si loo yareeyo burburka daran ee caabuqa.
Si kastaba ha noqotee, qaadashada steroids-ka xad-dhaafka ah wax faa'iido ah kuma lahan cudurka sambabka ee daran ee bukaannada SARS iyo COVID-19.
Taa bedelkeeda, waxay keeni karaan waxyeelo daran, gaar ahaan osteonecrosis, taas oo keenta saameynta cudurka.
