BAngiotensin enzyme 2 (ACE2) waa enzyme ku xidhan dusha sare (membranes cell) ee unugyada ku jira sambabada, xididdada dhiigga, wadnaha, kelyaha, iyo mindhicirka.
ACE2 waxay xakameysaa waxqabadka enzyme-ka la xiriira iskudhafka (ACE) iyadoo la yareynayo xaddiga angiotensin-II iyo kor u qaadista Ang (1-7) taasoo ka dhigaysa bartilmaameed muhiim u ah daaweynta cudurrada wadnaha. ACE2 waxay sidoo kale u shaqeysaa sidii habka gelitaanka unugyada qaar ka mid ah coronaviruses.
Enzyme-ka aadanaha waxaa lagu magacaabaa hACE2.
Enzyme-ka Angiotensin 2 waa zinc-ka ku jira ironloenzyme oo ku yaal dusha sare ee endothelial iyo unugyada kale.
Waxyaabaha ay ka kooban tahay ACE2 waxay ka kooban yihiin N-terminal peptidase M2 domain iyo C-terminal collectrin renal amino acid transport domain.
ACE2 waa nooc ka mid ah borotiinka xuubka, oo leh qayb enzymatically firfircoon oo ka soo horjeeda dusha sare ee unugyada sanbabada iyo unugyada kale ee jirka.
Qaybta ka baxsan unugyada ACE2 waxaa laga soo saaraa qaybta unugyada by enzyme loo yaqaan 'blood-flow', iyo natiijada borotiinka dheefshiidka waxaa loo wareejiyaa dhiigga ugu dambeyntii wuxuu ku jiraa kaadida.
ACE2 wuxuu ku jiraa xubno badan: ACE2 wuxuu ku dhexeeyaa maqaarka ugu badan ee unugyada alveolar ee unugyada sambabada nooca II, enterocytes-ka xiidmaha hoose, unugyada wadnaha iyo wadnaha iyo unugyada muruqyada jilicsan ee xubnaha badankood.
Calaamadaha ACE2 MRNA waxaa laga heli karaa maskaxda maskaxda, hypotamalamus straitum iyo briainstem.
Shaqada ugu horeysa ee ACE2 waa inay u shaqeyso sidii heerka isku dheelitirka ACE.
ACE waxay hoos u dhigtaa hormoonka angiotensin I ee vasoconstricting angiotensin II.
ACE2 waxay isku xirtaa carboxyl-terminal amino acid phenylalanine oo ka timaada angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) waxayna hydrolyses u sameysaa angiotensin vasodilator (1-7), (H-Asp-Arg -Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
ACE2 waxay sidoo kale baabi'in kartaa peptides kale oo ay ka mid yihiin [des-Arg9] -bradykinin, apelin, neurotensin, dynorphin A, iyo ghrelin.
ACE2 waxay sidoo kale xakameysaa gaadiidka xuubka ee amino acid-ka dhexdhexaadka ah ee SLC6A19 waxayna la xiriirtaa cudurka Hartnup.
Sida borotiinka transmembrane, ACE2 wuxuu u shaqeeyaa sidii waddo weyn oo loo maro unugyada (Cell) ee qaar ka mid ah coronavirus-yada, oo ay ku jiraan HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (virus-ka sababa SARS); iyo SARS-CoV-2 (virus-ka sababa COVID-19).
Isku darka protein spike s1 ee SARS-CoV iyo SARS-CoV2 waxay isku daraan ACE2 ee xerada unugyada taas oo keenta in endocytosis iyo translocation ee cudurka iyo sidoo kale virus-ka ku dhaca endosome-ka oo ku jira unugyada.
