Marka ay neefsashadu soo baxdo, inta badan waxay ku dhacaan dhulka ama dusha sare halkii ay ka ahaan lahaayeen kuwa cudurka kala qaado.
Dadka waxaa laga qaadi karaa cudurka marka ay taabtaan meelo wasakhaysan, indhaha, sanka, ama afka.
